        "subject": "LU-4803 ofd: skip orphan cleanup when inject OI error",
        "message": "LU-4803 ofd: skip orphan cleanup when inject OI error\n\nWhen inject OI error for simulating some failure cases, the object\nmay be mapped to invalid local target (inode for ldiskfs), so skip\nthe orphan cleanup in OSP to avoid unexpected warning or destroy.\n\nLustre-commit: I8e0a8a9bb4ae584fc8f40f894a19e8f10aa24c10\nLustre-change: http://review.whamcloud.com/9759\n\nTest-Parameters: testlist=sanity-scrub\nSigned-off-by: Fan Yong <fan.yong@intel.com>\nSigned-off-by: Lai Siyao <lai.siyao@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I1882fda921502367bb995921e176bc20fb21155f\n"
